Class ReportItemToDTOMapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.oapen.irusuk.dataingestion.jpa.ReportItemToDTOMapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ToPersistableEntitiesMapper<ItemDTO,EventDTO>

    public class ReportItemToDTOMapper
extends java.lang.Object
implements ToPersistableEntitiesMapper<ItemDTO,EventDTO>
    Maps a ReportItem to a (persistable) Item and a (persistable) List of Events

    Takes an IpLookupService to enrich IRUSUK data with geolocation data for ip addresses. IRUS UK data does contain ip addresses along with originating country data for requests, but without precise geographical data (city, latitude/longitude) so these finer grained fields are provided by IpLookupService during the mapping process.

    acdhirr
